## HTTP REQUEST
```
GET /networks/[id]/clients/[mac]/splashAuthorizationStatus
```

## PARAMETERS
**None**

## SAMPLE REQUEST
```
curl -L -H 'X-Cisco-Meraki-API-Key: <key>' -X GET -H 'Content-Type: application/json' 'https://dashboard.meraki.com/api/v0/networks/[id]/clients/[mac]/splashAuthorizationStatus'
```
## SAMPLE RESPONSE
```
Successful HTTP Status: 200
{
  "ssids": {
    "0": {
      "isAuthorized": true,
      "authorizedAt": "2017-07-19 16:24:13 UTC",
      "expiresAt": "2017-07-20 16:24:13 UTC"
    },
    "2": {
      "isAuthorized": false
    }
  }
}
```

## HTTP REQUEST
